<note id="fs-idm212975184" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm224191008"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 7.5 World War I: Military and Diplomacy</para>
<para id="fs-idm242276672"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm212578032"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 7F Explain the causes and consequences of U.S. involvement in World War I</para>
<para id="fs-idm230483392"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 7.3.II.B</para>
<para id="fs-idm218710880"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
